[[Professor/Legends|Professor]] '''Bin Binnari''' was a member of the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Republic's]] [[Astrographic Survey Institute]].

Professor Binnari compiled the Institute's report on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] of [[Leria Kerlsil]] with the help of [[New Republic Intelligence Service|New Republic Intelligence]] agent [[Shella Harin]].

